    "revision": "RevA2",
    "critical_fixes_revA2": [
        "U1 ESP32-S3-PICO-1 pad nets corrected to package pin numbers from Espressif datasheet.",
        "Camera D9-D5 are on GPIO10-14 / U1 pads 15-19; GPIO33-37/U1 pads 38-42 are left unconnected for N8R8 octal PSRAM.",
        "U1 pad46 is 3V3 CPU supply, not camera data. U1 pads55/56 are VDDA tied to 3V3, not GND.",
        "U0TXD/U0RXD moved to U1 pads49/50. LED_STATUS moved to GPIO47/U1 pad37.",
        "All support IC/passive pads now have explicit net assignments, except intended NC/DNP/mechanical pads."
    ]
